---
#------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# YAML Aliases to simplify maintenance

anchorLinks:
  - link: &grafana-home
      url: "https://grafana.com/"
      params: "time"
      
#------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# YAML anchors for colors
portLabelColor: &portLabelColor
  thresholdPatterns:
    - {color: "black", pattern: '.*up.*'}
    - {color: "white", pattern: '.*down.*'}

portFillColor: &portFillColor
  thresholdPatterns:
    - {color: "green", pattern: '.*up.*'}
    - {color: "red", pattern: '.*down.*'}

portStrokeColor: &portStrokeColor
  thresholdPatterns:
    - {color: "green", pattern: '.*up.*'}
    - {color: "red", pattern: '.*down.*'}

portRateColor: &portRateColor
  gradientMode: "hue"
  thresholds:
    - {color: "green", level: 0}
    - {color: "red", level: 3000000}

portRateLabel: &portRateLabel
  separator: "replace"
  units: "bps"
  decimalPoints: 1

#------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Panel Config



cellIdPreamble: "cell-"
cells:
